{"tid":838640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強颱風「潭美」逼近 或橫掃日本全國","createTime":"2018-09-27T09:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T07:56:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a057526ba65d642a4923aa61db4103330fd11d","tid":838640,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sxHKetRECpSaUw_RdErKaw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2018-09/fb716ca0-c210-11e8-8dff-fdd1fea1f097\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsxHKetRECpSaUw_RdErKaw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-09%2Ffb716ca0-c210-11e8-8dff-fdd1fea1f097&h=8458a744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從外太空拍攝潭美颱風<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】超強颱風「潭美」（Trami）周三下午在沖繩以南海域向北移動，預料周六至周日接近沖繩、奄美，周日稍晚逼近西日本，其後有可能橫掃日本。日本氣象廳呼籲民眾留意最新情況，並做好防風準備。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報道，氣象廳以「大型、威力非常強」形容「潭美」。周三傍晚六時左右，潭美在沖繩南方海上往北前進，移動速度緩慢。預計潭美周六左右保持強勁威力接近沖繩、奄美一帶。之後路徑轉向東北逼近西日本，前進速度加快，可能從九州到北海道橫掃全日本，並帶來暴風和大雨。<br />\n<br />\n截至周三晚上九時，近中心最大風力時速一百六十二公里，最大瞬間風力時速二百一十六公里。日本氣象廳表示，沖繩周五會颳暴風，海上將出現猛烈風浪。周日西日本風雨可能增強。<br />\n<br />\n駐守國際太空站的德國太空人格斯特（Alexander Gerst），在Twitter發布他看到的潭美風眼照片，表示看起來「像是有人從地球拔走一個巨型塞子」。他指潭美「勢不可擋」，祝福地上的人安全。<br />\n<br />\nCNN氣象學家賽特指出，潭美在周三停滯不前，走勢不明，氣象學家們對其路徑抱觀望態度。賽特指估計，若這場風暴按照預想的方向發展，可能會在四天內，在日本南面登陸前減弱一些，但威力仍相當於美國標準的四級颶風。<br />\n<br />\n潭美威力一度達美國標準的五級颶風，已是本月第三個強度達五級的西太平洋風暴。月中同級颶風「山竹」蹂躪菲律賓呂宋、香港、澳門和廣東一帶，在菲律賓造成百多人死亡或失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8-%E6%BD%AD%E7%BE%8E-%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%91-%E6%88%96%E6%A9%AB%E6%8E%83%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B-221123087.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8-%25E6%25BD%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E-%25E9%2580%25BC%25E8%25BF%2591-%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E6%258E%2583%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B-221123087.html&d=MMfzIUeDDF2SfcWtqNfQN8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1bf9a49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8-%E6%BD%AD%E7%BE%8E-%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%91-%E6%88%96%E6%A9%AB%E6%8E%83%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B-221123087.html</a>"},{"pid":"59d65b2a7853f3b5201d3d85614cef6254e4b2da","tid":838640,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"（警報）中國人國慶旅遊目的地：日本首次列第一　香港第三<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bBLFrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bBLFrS</a>"},{"pid":"6e801e59346763e4501f7f526c3b4fb431518f16","tid":838640,"uid":68620,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"好心就吹去上海同北京啦，天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c864bb91dd9d8d1628c37ff65a8c02ac53dca5","tid":838640,"uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6e801e59346763e4501f7f526c3b4fb431518f16","tid":838640,"uid":68620,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"好心就吹去上海同北京啦，天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"中國人:  上海真是福地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fee99cc61f96a12354d41fa63a6ef70f0dfa684","tid":838640,"uid":132038,"like":59,"dislike":8,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6ad69f8a81f202fb199b19ad6c332d17b3007e1","tid":838640,"uid":200474,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"做咩又吹去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfeb3df569c3269558c38606d92f56d775a1426e","tid":838640,"uid":4180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"